1. The program renames photo files found in a pointed by user folder to its (photo) taking date/time.

2. User can set date/time pattern to new file name.

3. Program renames file found recursively in all found inner directories.

4. User can set max depth for scanning of inner directories.

5. User can set extensions of photo files to rename.

6. Program renames NEF parameters file as well.

7. Program supports dry run.